            <div class="privacyText">
              For site security purposes and to ensure that service remains available to all users, the eiNetwork uses software programs to monitor network traffic to identify unauthorized
              attempts to upload or change information or otherwise cause damage.  Except for these purposes, no other attempts are made to identify individual users or their usage habits.
