        <div id="privacy_database" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <div class="EIN-col-m-12" style="height:5px"></div>
            <div class="privacyText">
              To access databases - to which eiNetwork subscribes for the use of library users - remotely (from outside a participating library), users must enter their library card numbers to help
              ensure that the system is used only by Allegheny County residents.  This information is not provided to database vendors, which are not able to obtain information relating to individual
              users of the database via eiNetwork.
              <br><br>
              The eiNetwork does not retain data relating to searches of other databases, such as newspaper, magazine, or encyclopedic databases, licensed by the eiNetwork.
